title: Nick Cannon celebrates women in his TV show, music
text:
Nick Cannon celebrates women in his TV show, music 5:10pm GMT - 02:39 
The TV-host dedicates an episode of his hip-hop comedy show ''Wild 'n Out'' to women's empowerment. Elly Park reports. ▲ Hide Transcript ▶ View Transcript
